2003-09-21  Puja Gupta  <puja@icon.fsl.cs.sunysb.edu>, Jay, Hari, Mohammad.

	* inode.c: removed extra bstart, and comments.

	* file.c (unionfs_readdir): Added a bindex++ to {un,re}-reverted code.
	Works now!! ;-)

